# Site Configuration (Google Sheets CSV)
# Set this to your Google Sheets CSV URL (published as web)
# Format: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/SHEET_ID/pub?gid=TAB_ID&single=true&output=csv
# Example:
