# Instructions:
# 1. Go to your Google Sheet "Config" tab
# 2. Go to File > Share > Publish to web
# 3. Select your "Config" tab
# 4. Choose "Comma-separated values (.csv)" format
# 5. Copy the URL and paste it above
# 6. Make sure your sheet has columns: config_key, config_value
